Steven Tandy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steven_Tandy 0 Steven Tandy (born 23 October 1952, Sydney, Australia) is an Australian stage, television and film actor, best known for playing Tom Sullivan, the second eldest son in the classic Australian television series The Sullivans.
